===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}} 
# Neither [[good]] nor [[bad]]; [[tolerable]], [[passable]], [[indifferent]].
#:''The dessert was pretty good, but the meal was '''so-so'''.''

====Synonyms====
*(''neither good nor bad''): [[average]], [[fair]], [[meh]], [[mediocre]], [[middling]], [[lackluster]], [[okay]]

